Author: 2017easyguide
Title: Easy Guide
Body: Hello and nice to meet you! Let us introduce ourselves!  EasyGuide is a touristic StartUp, uniting travellers from all around the Globe who wish to see new places on their own without the help of expensive agencies. With the project EasyGuide you will be able not only to save your money and nerves, but also to find interesting friends! Just register and start looking for companions to visit sightseeings and share the cost of renting a car, a boat or even a helicopter!   Our site:  http://guide-easy.com/
